To remove a server from the storage pool

* Remove a server from the storage pool using the following command: +
 +
# gluster peer detach _SERVER_ +
 +
For example, to remove server4 from the trusted storage pool, run the
following command: +
 +
# gluster peer detach server4 +
 +
Detach successful +
 +

